OL,3,CReduction in VAT rates in next week's
OL,4,Cbudget 'vital' for their survival
OL,6,FThe hospitality industry along with
OL,7,Fthe fast food sector have called for a
OL,8,Freduction in VAT rates at next week's
OL,9,Fbudget.
OL,11,FThey say a change is vital for their
OL,12,Fsurvival with rates across the border
OL,13,Fin the republic set to be slashed next
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FAmid all the talk about rising taxes
OL,17,Ffrom the Treasury this is a call to do
OL,18,Fthe complete opposite.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
