OL,6,FWillie Jack has owned pubs for
OL,7,Fdecades, he would like to see a
OL,8,Freduction in VAT to stay competitive
OL,9,Fwith counterparts in the republic.
OL,11,FClick here to read about other
OL,12,Findustries that could be impacted by
OL,13,Fthe incoming Autumn Budget
OL,15,FHe said: "Our little group of
OL,16,Fcompanies, and that's a couple of
OL,17,Fpubs, and a coffee shop, and an off-
OL,18,Fsales, probably pays over two million
OL,19,Fin tax to the revenue every year.
