OL,6,F"So I think we make a very big
OL,7,Fcontribution. When you're in the
OL,8,Fhospitality business, we like a level
OL,9,Fplaying field.
OL,11,F"And unfortunately, in the North, we
OL,12,Fdon't have one. When you've got a
OL,13,Fdifferent rate of VAT over a an
OL,14,Finvisible line in a field in North
OL,15,FMonaghan, it's not fair."
OL,17,FThe rate in the republic is already
OL,18,Flower at 13.5% for hospitality.
OL,20,FThat will fall to 9% next July on food.
