OL,6,FFood To Go Association, Michael
OL,7,FHenderson said: "We just see European
OL,8,Fcountries like Germany, who is
OL,9,Fdropping their VAT rate from 17% to 7%
OL,10,Fin January because of the pressure of
OL,11,Fsharing a land border with other
OL,12,Fcountries with a lower VAT rate.
OL,14,F"Come July next year, we will be
OL,15,Fsharing a land border with the
OL,16,FRepublic of Ireland with a 11% deficit
OL,17,Fin VAT, which will cripple our small
OL,18,Fbusinesses in Northern Ireland."
